snippet.title: CIRCLE OF FOOTBALL [Announce Trailer - June 2020]
snippet.description:
Circle of Football Early Access is live on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1245570/Circle_of_Football/
It will be free for a limited time and it will remain free for those who will download it during the free period of time. It's a game for everyone, who likes soccer or not. You can play 1vs1 and 2vs2 online in competitive modes, as well as local multiplayer matches. Well, try it, and make us dream!
